sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Institute Holidays Management Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open institute holidays page
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW->>DB: Query institutes and current institute holiday events
    DB-->>LW: Options and event list
    LW-->>UI: Render institute selector and events

    User->>UI: Change institute / edit holiday rows
    UI->>LW: updatedInstituteId() and form changes
    LW->>DB: Re-query events for selected institute
    DB-->>LW: Filtered holiday list
    LW-->>UI: Re-render event rows

    User->>UI: Save changes
    UI->>LW: save()
    LW->>DB: Upsert holiday events + delete removed rows
    DB-->>LW: Persist completed
    LW-->>UI: Success toast

    User->>UI: Delete one event
    UI->>LW: deleteEvent(id)
    LW->>DB: Delete event row
    DB-->>LW: Deleted
    LW-->>UI: Refresh list
